      },
      "writtenOn": "2018-02-13T21:45:11Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Why did CrashReportDatabaseMac (and CrashReportDatabaseWin in the other file) need to be exposed more broadly? Seems unnecessary given that these two classes aren’t declared except in their respective implementation files.",
      "revId": "74c258ec4fa59f33c8d97f8d06c7736111c95b46",
      "serverId": "3ce6091f-6c88-37e8-8c75-72f92ae8dfba",
